3. [Contact Us](#contact-us)

## Installation

### Download from the App Store (iPhone and iPad)

1. Open the App Store on your iPhone or iPad.
2. Search for "AI Language Translator Offline" in the search bar.
3. Tap on the app icon in the search results.
4. On the app page, tap the "Get" or "Download" button.
5. Authenticate with your Apple ID, if prompted.
6. Wait for the app to download and install on your device.
7. Once installed, the app icon will appear on your home screen.

## Features

AI Language Translator Offline offers a range of features to enhance your Language Translation and Learning experience. Explore the following capabilities:

### Offline Translation

AI Powered Language Translation works with completely AI Trained Language Models. Totally we support 37 Languages in offline. All you need to download the Language models when you start your app first time or via 
settings page where you can able to download or delete the langauge required for translation. In settings page, we have two option, Download languages or delete languages. Since, this is offline AI powered
Translation which works pretty fast even in conversation and Transcribe Features. 

### Voice to Text Features ( Transcribe and Conversation )

Now, you can record your voice and translate into your desired language without depending on internet. Even you can record it in low decibel and noisy environment with much accuracy and fast. You can tap
your mic once to start converting from source to target language and tap the mic again to stop the translation via voice. we have live ultra fast transcribe page where you can try different country level
accent and translate to your desired language without any delay or internet.

### AI Powered Image to Translator

With our Advanced AI powered Image to Translate Generator where you can lively click a picture and translate it to your desired language without depending on the internet. we support 37 Target Languages. 

### History

You can save all your translation in the history page for future references. Also, you can have dedicated paste and copy buttons for export and import the content. 

